2001-07-05    <majkel.kretschmar@epost.de>



	* elks2001/uc_string.e: Started experimental implementation of

	UC_STRING based upon ELKS2001 STRING proposal. implemented

	features in sections Initialization, Basic sepicifiers, and

	Measurement.



2001-07-02    <majkel.kretschmar@epost.de>



	* uc_character_ref.e: added `as_hexadecimal' and `and

	as_character'. modified `out' so it can print characters greater

	than 0xffff in hexadecimal representation. references to

	character's maximum code not longer hard wired, using now platform.



